# CSS layer

All visuals live here. React and Elements must not re-style.

## BEM + tokens

```css
/* ✅ GOOD */
.rgrm-button--primary {
  color: var(--rgrm-button-primary-color, inherit);
  padding-block: var(--rgrm-button-primary-padding-block-start, 0);
}

/* ❌ BAD — hardcoded colour */
.rgrm-button--primary {
  color: #05102e;
}
```

- Use semantic tokens (`--rgrm-theme-*`, `--rgrm-{component}-*`)
- Missing tokens: `var(--rgrm-*, <fallback>)` + document in `docs/token-proposals/<name>.md`
- Prefer fluid `clamp()` tokens for scalable properties

## Package registration

When adding a component:

1. `src/<name>/index.css`
2. `@import` in `src/index.css`
3. lightningcss line in `package.json` `scripts.build`
4. Exports: `"./<name>"` and `"./<name>.css"`

Run `pnpm lint:css` — Stylelint must pass.
